com.tinkerpop.blueprints.oupls.jung

Class GraphJung<T extends Graph>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.blueprints.oupls.jung.GraphJung<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WrapperGraph<T>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.DirectedGraph<Vertex,Edge>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph<Vertex,Edge>, edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Hypergraph<Vertex,Edge>

    public class GraphJung<T extends Graph>
extends Object
implements edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.DirectedGraph<Vertex,Edge>, WrapperGraph<T>
    An implementation of the JUNG graph interface provided by Blueprints graph. In this way, a Blueprints graph is modeled as a JUNG graph. This JUNG model can be used with any algorithms/tools that require a JUNG graph.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
